{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481170/extras/Gif_Intro_ShuffleTactics_Reduced.gif?t=1740146145\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by timeless classics such as <i>Final Fantasy Tactics</i> and indie sensations like <i>Slay the Spire</i>, <i>Shuffle Tactics</i> brings tactical deckbuilding to the next level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <br>Defend the <strong>Kingdom of Asteria</strong> from the corruption of the <strong>Glimmer Curse</strong> in this roguelike tactical RPG. Build your best deck, obtain super-powerful relics, and choose the best sidekick to help you in your quest to overthrow the <strong>evil King Ogma</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481170/extras/Gif_1.gif?t=1740146145\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unleash your best combos in <strong>strategic turn-based battles</strong>, but beware the curses that will weigh down on you throughout your journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Outwit the <strong>Corrupted Dwellers</strong> with cunning battle tactics and razor-sharp positioning. Whether you are a veteran player or a neophyte, you must think strategically and use all the tools <i>Shuffle Tactics</i> offers to prevail in your ordeal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you lean on your martial skills or choose to harness the dangerous powers of the Glimmer?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481170/extras/Gif_3.gif?t=1740146145\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Demo Content</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as <strong>two characters</strong>, each with their own abilities: the <strong>Doberknight</strong>, a sword-hurling powerhouse that can kick foes into optimal positions and spread fire to surrounding tiles or foes alike, along with <strong>Catalina</strong>, a master of elemental magic who builds Mana Pylons around the battlefield and charges them with devastating spells</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet <strong>five sidekicks</strong>, each with different skills to aid you in battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Forge your path across <strong>two biomes</strong>: the dilapidated outskirts of a Capital known as The Deluge, and The Snarl, a lush forest teeming with menacing creatures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge <strong>four bosses</strong>, randomly selected for each biome</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481170/extras/Gif_1.3.gif?t=1740146145\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481170/extras/WishlistNowSTv2.gif?t=1740146145\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3481170?t=1740146145","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481170/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740146145","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481170/503b2cff32b516100ff28de749dae0e50ba4d76f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740146145","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481170/503b2cff32b516100ff28de749dae0e50ba4d76f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740146145","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img c